properties.name: Kelly Armstrong
properties.biography: Kelly Armstrong is the Republican representative from North Dakota's At-Large Congressional District in the U.S. House. Armstrong was elected to the office on November 6, 2018. Armstrong is a former Republican member of the North Dakota State Senate, representing District 36 from 2012 to 2018.
